## 1.单机JVM

### 1.1 Thread-Thread.sleep方法

```
public static void main(String[] args) {
    Runnable runnable = () -> {
        while (true){
            try {
                Thread.sleep(2000);
                System.out.println("定时任务执行");
            } catch (InterruptedException e) {
                e.printStackTrace();
            }
        }
    };
    Thread thread = new Thread(runnable);
    thread.start();
}
```
